flowchart TD
    CLI[CLI Entry Point] --> SRV[HTTP Server]
    CLI --> MCP[MCP Server]
    CLI --> WATCH[File Watcher]

    SRV --> ROUTES[REST Routes]
    SRV --> WS[WebSocket Manager]
    SRV --> STATIC[Static Assets]
    SRV --> SROUTES[Session Routes]

    MCP --> TOOLS[MCP Tools]
    MCP --> STOOLS[Session Tools]
    MCP --> SCHEMAS[Schemas]
    MCP --> RES[Resources]

    TOOLS --> GHOST[Ghost Store]
    STOOLS --> SESS[Session Store]
    GHOST --> WS
    SESS --> WS

    ROUTES --> DIAG[Diagram Service]
    ROUTES --> GHOST
    SROUTES --> SESS

    DIAG --> PARSER[Graph Parser]
    DIAG --> ANNOT[Annotations]
    DIAG --> VALID[Validator]
    DIAG --> COLLAPSE[Collapser]
    PARSER --> EDGES[Edge Parser]
    PARSER --> SERIAL[Serializer]

    WATCH --> DIAG
    WATCH --> WS

    PROJ[Project Manager] --> DISC[Discovery]

    WS --> BROWSER[Browser UI]
    STATIC --> BROWSER

    BROWSER --> REND[Renderer + SVG]
    BROWSER --> PANUI[Pan/Zoom + Interaction]
    BROWSER --> EDITUI[Editor + Inline Edit]
    BROWSER --> GHOSTUI[Ghost Paths UI]
    BROWSER --> HEATUI[Heatmap UI]
    BROWSER --> SESSUI[Session Player]
    BROWSER --> TREEUI[File Tree]

